You are looking at NETUTIL's Connection data entry screen.

This popup allows you to edit Connection data associated
with a vnode.  This includes the type of connection (Global
or Private), Network address, Protocol, and Listen Address.

Menu Operations

        MENU COMMAND    SYNOPSIS
        ------------    --------

        Save            Saves all edits.

        ListChoices     List the choices possible for the Protocol
			field.

        Cancel          Cancels the edit operation without saving any
                        potentially changed fields.

        Help            Displays this help screen.
